author: wmtan
body:
PR #9429 fixed build errors in CMSSW_7_5_ROOT5_X by updating checksums.
This PR simply makes the ROOT5 checksums known in the ROOT6 release (7_5_X).
It also replaces a class name with its typedef to be consistent with CMSSW_7_5_ROOT5_X.
title: Make ROOT5 checksums known in ROOT6
